Key: Building-admin.com is for a relaxed administrator. We invite you to try it out!

Values.ro: Building-admin.com inseamna un administrator relaxat. Te invitam sa incerci si tu!
Values.en: Building-admin.com is for a relaxed administrator. We invite you to try it out!

Key: We aim to help building administrators

Values.ro: Platforma noastra online isi doreste sa ajute administratorii. Acestua vor putea pastra intr-un sigur loc toata documentatia despre locatari si cheltuielile asociatiei. De asemeana, listele de cheltuieli se vor crea mai usor si mai rapid.
Values.en: We aim to help building administrators to better organize thier documents, to have them all in one place. Also the billing tables can be created faster and easier.

Values.ro: Administrea cheltuilelile de bloc rapid, usor, de oriunde si oricand. Program de administrare contabila pentru asociatiile de proprietari.
Values.en: Managing building administration billings, anytime, anywhere, on any device. Building administration and much more.
